headline: 2 Stocks That Turned $1,000 Into More Than $8,000 in 10 Years to Buy and Hold
summary: Intuitive Surgical and Veeva Systems have crushed the market since 2015.  The average stock market return over the past few decades (without accounting for inflation) is around 10%.  Two examples are Intuitive Surgical (NASDAQ: ISRG) and Veeva Systems (NYSE: VEEV).
